Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SIGN: Little Haruhi's U2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to return this \NDVD to Wataru's store.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall go return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you had it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roughly 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it may be closer to 3 years by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurrying at this point is moot, but \NI just have to get this returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why a potted plant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling luck's not with me today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:56.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Closed due to special circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luck really isn't with me today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, it's not like \Nanything unfortunate happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:16.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:22.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:25.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who is there to support his mistress \Nin all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.51,0:01:27.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.66,0:01:31.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is about a boy who fights and puts \Nhis life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:35.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Young Sir does not understand \Nwhat is in a woman's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Young Sir, you cur!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teehee.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:48.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:48.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:55.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:55.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:58.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:58.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:03.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:03.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:07.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:07.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:10.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:10.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:16.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:16.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:26.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:26.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:32.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:32.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:39.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:39.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:44.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:44.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:51.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:51.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:58.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:58.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've Never Had the Trouble \Nof Being Too Popular
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Hayate! That DVD was actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies. Wataru's \Nstore was closed today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I left it in the return box.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! I let my guard down \Nand didn't prep a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To what do we owe the pleasure today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to ask "to what"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to check on Nagi, 'cause I heard \Nshe hasn't been to school at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more of this needless conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wonderful tea will get cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ice tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lingering summer heat is \Nstill ruthless, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering how hot it is now in September,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how hot it'll get \Nin October and November.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would ya wonder that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was good. Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that, it's \Nactually autumn already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to autumn, \Nit's the season of eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, because it's the season \Nwhere you get beat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autumn, the season of beating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Falter and ya lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have confidence in yer own material!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya got a new openin' line?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening line?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it a new careless thing you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my stole...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your stole?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a new stole, but \Nsomewhere, I carelessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You left it and forgot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then I'll go look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I do not really care \Nif it is lost for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It only cost about 50 million yen, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look for it right \Naway, on the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is such a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course! My Hayate is the \Nworld's most kind and dependable man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:04.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I recall, Isumi was resting \Nin the guest bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today sure was rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to sleep on days like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And right as I was saying that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,here's a stole that'll \Nmake the perfect blanket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll pick it up with \Nthese claws that shred cloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Tama! That stole cost 50 million and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch Isumi's stole!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking of touching Isumi's personal \Nbelonging, when you're only a pet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wataru? When did he get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even {\i1}I{\i0} don't often get to touch \NIsumi's personal belongings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her personal belonging...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How long have you been \Nthere, you butler-in-debt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been here the whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did you see that just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By "that just now", do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:05:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-So, you know...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that almost pathological \Nbehavior unique to adolescents
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where you happen to come upon \Nan object that was worn by the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,girl you like and you get \Nthe urge to sniff it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's normal when you consider \Nwhat 13-year-olds do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like tell Nagi and Isumi what you saw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sanzenin butler does not do things \Nthat would embarrass a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a Sanzenin pet {\i1}would{\i0} do things \Nthat would embarrass a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, weren't you not going to speak, \Nbecause it would ruin your image?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the girls that I \Ndon't want to ruin my image.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I {\i1}want{\i0} to ruin my image for boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rarr! Rarr! Rarr!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This anime is geared towards boys, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm gonna get right to \Ntelling the young ladies
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about this stinking brat's weird behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,using a dying message from Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, if Isumi finds out, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea Wataru was \Nthat kind of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is worse than an insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry. Please leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks, butler-in-debt. \NI'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Incidentally, what \Nare you doing here, Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm here because that \Nidiot Nagi returned a DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I'd gone to the \Ntrouble of giving to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I came to give it to her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so glad! Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! First, I'll \Nspread the rumor on the net
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and build it up so the Miss hears about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've started numerous threads \Nthat went on to become famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries! I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll build up the hype myself \Nby using different IPs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make the thread really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, enough with making \Ntrouble for our guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I will show you no mercy, \Neven if you {\i1}are{\i0} the Miss's pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Tama has reconsidered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still can't face Isumi, \Nso you give it to her for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. I am honored to be of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:31.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ayasaki Hayate... If I \Ncould be a man like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:35.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Little Wataru kept his steady \Ngaze on Hayate's back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Isumi. Your stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad he was \Nable to find it, Isumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is all thanks to my dear Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, where's Sakuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left just earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,complaining she had no one to make jabs at.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I shall be taking \Nmy leave soon as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, please be very \Ncareful on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dear Hayate, you seem \Nrather happy for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am. A certain person thanked \Nme for a little something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had a string of mishaps lately, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this morning, I got ran over by a truck
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and people were giving me unfriendly looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It made me feel a bit down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it was just \Nmy imagination, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunate things have happened \Nto me ever since I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I think it was just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dear Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my thanks for the stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this will make \Nthings somewhat better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know that I \Nlove you, my dear Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The romantic comedy turn \Nof events to be continued!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real love.\N({\u1}Ri{\u0}aru ra{\u1}bu{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brassiere complex!\N({\u1}Bu{\u0}rajaa konpurekku{\u1}su{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know that I \Nlove you, my dear Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Maybe it's just that kids love me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It turns out that we have \Na wholesome protagonist,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who doesn't consider kids to \Nbe possible romantic partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been awake this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw them yesterday, it looked \Nto me like they were embracing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it bothers you that much, \Nwhy not ask them yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ask and Isumi really does love Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Hayate already in love with \Nme, it would mean hurting Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it may be some kind of misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a high probability that \NIsumi has fallen in love with Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Hayate is the \Ncoolest man in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it will be a serious problem
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if the coolest man in the universe \Nwere making a pass at Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would never happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Hayate to pursue some \Ngirl other than me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For him to make a pass at Isumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For him to fall for some other girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to go see Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a little question for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, do you, um... love Isumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do love Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously in love with Isumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me! After what you did yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Well, I don't think I'm \Nactually {\i1}in{\i0} love with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then are you just playing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you were just toying with \NIsumi when you did that yesterday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, I play with \NSakuya more than Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I would like to \Nplay more with Isumi, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J... J...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't crack eggs using my head. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I misjudged you, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did I do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I-I wouldn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be because Isumi confessed \Nto me that she loved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isumi said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's so cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be that kids just love me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe I'd make a good \Npreschool teacher or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:55.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must... do something about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:57.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Video Rental\NV Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,DX Animation\NTama's Sinister Design!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do men want to watch such things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:09.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've been looking at it for some \N30 minutes yourself, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:14.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Young Sir is still a child, so \NI'm sure he has no interest in girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:17.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but will he eventually want \Nto watch things like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:20.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! I'm sure only a portion of men do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:21.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Surely, the Young Sir will not...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:29.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Do Not Enter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:27.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he has not set foot \Noutside since last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:29.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What in the world could he be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am sorry, we are not open yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! Isumi couldn't possibly have \Nfeelings for the butler-in-debt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you sleep there like \Nyou've got no problems?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nagi, what the hell are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?! I've run away from home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heartbreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:01.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And in despair, the girl ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys can go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't tell Maria about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.20,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running away from home!!\N Don't look for me!!\NNagi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll have to look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to Isumi's place first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, if Miss Nagi has run \Naway from home, does that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She will be staying here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Miss Saki Kijima.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nagi is the one and only \Ngranddaughter of the Sanzenin family
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she is to be spending time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something should happen to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will not go unpunished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we'll get nowhere if we \Njust keep fighting like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to Isumi's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and ask her how she feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, Nagi has run away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, some dust got in my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't it possible you were \Nmistaken about what you saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true, them embracing would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss, so this is where you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to see Isumi the \Nmoment I disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh, yes, I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi can just take you for 150 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! M-Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I take him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I take my dear Hayate for 150 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thus, the romantic comedy has grown
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:34.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}into a muddy, icky, quagmire \Nof a love-hate drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the meantime, as for Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something about this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what? Huh? I've been left \Nalone somewhere along the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Video Rental\NV Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:18:00.63,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoplifting is a crime
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! What the heck is the big \Nidea of renting such boring DVDs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,0:17:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what's with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all just hyped up pieces of garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's my decision to make...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you listen to me carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is limited!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are countless masterpieces \Nin this world that must be seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are decisively lacking in "Gundam"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:10.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sieg Ze*n
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! "Gundam"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'll loan you all of it from \Nthe original series to "00"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! All of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't sleep, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sleep and watch it all, \Nlike your life depended on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Char's Counterattack" and \N"Turn A" are particularly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like he even understands!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't randomly loan out my DVDs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not doing it randomly! I've \Nselected masterpieces to loan out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing here anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I've run away \Nfrom home, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason you didn't want \Nto be at home to begin with
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was because that butler-in-debt \Nwas there, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, get your butt home already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that butler-in-debt's \Nnot at your house anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YOUNG SIR!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing bullying the Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wasn't really bullying her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the rate you are going, Isumi \Nwill come to hate you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Doooom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll just burn this damn store!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let it all burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You cannot do this! Young Sir! Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:22.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right around then, Saki was at the \Nmercy of two heartbroken children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:25.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now, next time, they \Nwill fight against a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru and Tarutaru
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a kitten. I don't have a name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky's so high up there again today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look! So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow, a kitten!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It warms my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hah, don't just let your heart be warmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you've got any compassion, feed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:02.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, you're really leaving?! \NColdhearted bastards! Hypocrites!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:08.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darn, the rain in the city is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:14.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But man, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, that's milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:25.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:28.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You weren't gonna give it to me, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:33.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mouth-to-mouth feeding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}C-Come on, bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:47.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-Hey, you okay? You got a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, Wataru, so this is where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you found the kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been worried and out looking for \Nit every time it rained, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:08.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bro, you've been looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. There, there. There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:17.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bro, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so this kitty's name is Tarutaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:25.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cute name!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:36.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-It's kind of lame, but \NI'll just let it lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:00.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Naida kokoro no ho ni kaze ga fuki-nuketetta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:00.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A breeze crossed the wilted sail of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:05.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimochi yureru soshite Lose My Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:05.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings waver and then I lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:08.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zutto kimi ga iru nara ii ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:08.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess if you'll always be here, it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:13.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore mo waruku wa nai So I Go Together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:13.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not so bad, so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:16.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tenki-yohou nante nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:16.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Weather forecasts don't exist
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zenbu kibun-shidai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all mood-dependent
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:21.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nanimo shinpai nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:21.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:24.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Makasete! Jiyuu-jizai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:24.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me! Perfectly free
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:26.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Keri-ageta kutsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:26.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,On the shoe that I kick up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:29.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Put A Wish" Zettai hareru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:29.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Put a Wish" it'll definitely clear up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:32.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kekka wa... I'm Looking At Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:32.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And the result is, I'm looking at nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:34.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mou ichido, yari-naoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:34.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time, a do-over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:38.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tama ni wa kakete-miyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:38.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try betting once in a while
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:42.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nee kimi ni yudanete-mitai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:42.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want to try entrusting you with it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:47.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sassou to kake-nukete To Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:47.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Running through gallantly, to fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:49.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Harema ga mieru The Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:49.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see a break in the weather, the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:51.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shinjiteta yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:51.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I had faith
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Soshite Make My Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I make my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:57.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sotto sashi-dasu kimi no te de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:57.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With the hand you quietly reach out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:02.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Muteki ni nareru kara So I Go Together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:02.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can become invincible, so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:10.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hoshi ga kirei da ashita mo hareru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:10.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stars so beautiful, it'll \Nbe clear again tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:30.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Best of luck tuning. I'm Nagi Sanzenin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sakuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.41,0:23:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't ya think I get too \Nlittle screen time on this show?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some characters show up every \Nweek for no good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.09,0:23:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's because you upstage \Nthe others when you show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler-in-debt, ya aren't \Ngonna gloss it over so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saku's the character that gets forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.55,0:23:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, whatever. Here's \Na risqué sexy shot of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Did ya sear that image into yer eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.47,0:23:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,240)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.77,0:24:00.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like me deserves to \Nget abandoned by the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:19.46,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of "Hayate \Nthe Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:03.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Being allowed to work in a \Ngrand mansion like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:05.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like a dream to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.71,0:24:08.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate probably hates me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.88,0:24:12.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you just test his love?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.31,0:24:13.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Test his love?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:15.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.60,0:24:16.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hearts Wavering".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:18.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to fake a kidnapping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.76,0:24:20.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You should not do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.49,0:24:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearts Wavering
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.46,0:24:22.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The clouds of war call to Hayate.
